Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/80284f68-2c32-42d3-b8a7-f234d017f92e) for commit 62bbf6d19813dde7b2487a48393c8831e64dacfd.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/c547b597-3f6b-45f5-b436-57839d2058b5/to/80284f68-2c32-42d3-b8a7-f234d017f92e) against commit 3ce43c18f614b76e161f911b75a3e1ef641620ff:
```diff
  Benchmark                                                  Metric         Change
  ================================================================================
- ~Mathlib.AlgebraicGeometry.AffineScheme                    instructions     2.9%
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.Analytic.Basic                           instructions   -17.1%
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.Analytic.Composition                     instructions   -57.7%
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.Analytic.Inverse                         instructions   -12.7%
- ~Mathlib.RepresentationTheory.GroupCohomology.Resolution   instructions     5.5%
```
